snippet.title: Amber Heard Has a Baby & A History of Domestic Violence 😳
snippet.description:
Amber Heard is now a mom, welcoming a daughter into the world by way of a surrogate. Many are concerned for the safety and well-being of the child, due to Heard's documented history of domestic violence. 


____________________________________________________
